definitions.definition: A unit of length equal to one thousandth of an inch (25.4 µm).
examples: We just wanted to take off a few thou , which we easily did with fine sandpaper.

main_definition: A unit of length equal to one thousandth of an inch (25.4 µm).

definitions.definition: A thousand , especially a thousand of some currency ( dollars , pounds sterling , etc.).
examples: Whoa there, big spender — that'll cost you a few thou . Are you sure you can afford it?

main_definition: ( slang ) A thousand , especially a thousand of some currency ( dollars , pounds sterling , etc.).
